  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study wants to investigate the hemodynamic changes in cardiopatic patients undergoing
      major non cardiac surgery, during and after the continuous infusion of levosimendan or
      dobutamine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
